primary.request: Check billing address and ownership details
primary.context: Caller had questions regarding a maintenance bill and wanted to verify account details
primary.detail: The agent successfully verified the caller and provided the address and owner name on file.

steps: Caller requested help with a maintenance bill.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number.
Agent verified identity after a name mismatch (Vincent vs Valerie).
Agent provided the address on file upon request.
Agent provided the owner name and contract details upon request.
Caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.

clarifications.note: Agent asked for spelling after name mismatch

corrections.note: User provided Valerie after agent flagged Vincent mismatch

actions.detail: Looked up account via phone number
Verified name and state of residence

insights.summary: The caller wanted to verify account details related to a maintenance bill. The agent successfully looked up the account, verified the caller, and provided the address and ownership information requested.
insights.verbatim: Whose address is on file? ... Who owns the unit?
